  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0baa\u0baf \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb0 \u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc7 \u0b86\u0ba9\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We are now experiencing the curse of cooperating with the Gotabhaya government to come to power - Ananda Thera from the beginning",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "We now face the curse of cooperating with the government led by President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa to come to power.",
        "Begging from other countries requires the president to resolve the issues or else resign.",
        "\"It does not matter to us who is the president and who is the prime minister, we need solutions to the problems facing the people,\" said Ananda Thera, the vicar of the Abhayarama Vihara.",
        "He was addressing a media briefing at the Abhayarama Temple on Sunday, the 26th.",
        "The people of Sri Lanka in the post-independence period are now facing the worst situation ever.",
        "The government came to power by making various promises. People expected a life of luxury.",
        "Not living a life of luxury is now perhaps even a great struggle to get food. It is true that we co-operated with the government led by President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa to come to power, but we do not deny it. We are now facing its curse.",
        "We have not mentioned anything about the administration of President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa so far. Now is the time to mention. It has been established by the President that the state administration cannot be carried forward in the best possible way.",
        "Never before in the history of Sri Lanka has the Sri Lankan people been fighting for food and the mother throwing her child into the river when she could not feed her children. Today the rich are affected and the poor are affected.",
        "The President's begging from other countries must protect the people of the country because those who have ruined the economy in the short term must be rewarded accordingly.",
        "We are very heartbroken. The future of the country will be completely destroyed if the present situation of the country is not resolved.",
        "The people formed a government led by President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa to great anticipation. The expectations of the people are completely gone. The president must find a solution to the problems if possible, otherwise he must resign.",
        "\"It does not matter to us who is the president or who is the prime minister at the moment. The people of the country need to live in peace. The problems facing the people need to be addressed,\" he said."
      ],
